

MinGW
=====
Download from http://sourceforge.net/projects/mingw/files/

Download the mingw-get-inst-XXXXXXX.exe file for an automated installation.
When prompted choose 
	* C Compiler
    * C++ Compiler
	* MSYS Basic 
	* MinGW Developer 	

Install MinGW

pthreads-w32
============
Download pthreads-w32 version 2.8.0 from http://sourceware.org/pthreads-win32/
ftp://sourceware.org/pub/pthreads-win32/pthreads-w32-2-8-0-release.tar.gz
tar xzvf pthreads-w32-2-8-0-release.tar.gz
cd pthreads-w32-2-8-0-release
make clean GC-static

libevent
========
Download from http://monkey.org/~provos/libevent/
http://monkey.org/~provos/libevent-2.0.10-stable.tar.gz
tar xzvf libevent-2.0.10-stable.tar.gz
cd libevent-2.0.10-stable.tar.gz
./configure --disable-openssl --disable-malloc-replacement
make

portaudio
=========
Download from http://www.portaudio.com/
http://www.portaudio.com/archives/pa_stable_v19_20071207.tar.gz
tar xzvf pa_stable_v19_20071207.tar.gz
cd portaudio
./configure
make

speex
=====
Download from www.speex.org
http://downloads.xiph.org/releases/speex/speex-1.2rc1.tar.gz
tar xzvf speex-1.2rc1.tar.gz
cd speex-1.2rc2
./configure
make

libpttp
=======
make -f Makefile.win